What the task wanted:-
Create a Bash script on App Server 2 (stapp02) that:
a> Compresses the website files from:
/var/www/html/news

b> Creates a ZIP archive named:
xfusioncorp_news.zip

c> Stores it locally in:
/archives

d> Copies the same zip file to the Storage Server (ststor1) under:
/archives

e> Runs without asking for a password
f> Can be executed by the App Server 2 user ( steve ).
g> Does not use 'sudo' inside the script.

